Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.73,0:01:39.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku had dispelled the barrier\naround his castle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:43.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}In otherwords, he had abandoned\nhis castle{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.67,0:01:46.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and hid himself somewhere else.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.78,0:01:51.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the past, no matterwhere\nhe hid,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.68,0:01:54.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I could sense the presence\nof his barrier.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.75,0:01:59.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But now, as though he\nhad disappeared from this world,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:01.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}there is absolutely no sign\nof Naraku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.42,0:02:05.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is something behind this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.30,0:02:12.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have had my soul collectors\nsearch forhis demonic aura.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.14,0:02:15.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But they cannot detect a barrier.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:20.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A demonic aura of such size...\nhow did he hide it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.02,0:02:37.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say, let's rest somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:39.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.73,0:02:41.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We just stopped to rest\nawhile ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.00,0:02:43.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But it's raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.03,0:02:46.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you, made of paper\nor somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.67,0:02:48.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can't call this "rain"!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.54,0:02:51.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not only that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:54.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Besides! You're riding that\nweird contraption.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.74,0:02:56.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've got it easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:57.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.48,0:03:02.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you ride this for a long time,\nyourbutt starts to hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:04.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.89,0:03:07.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why'd you make me\nsay it, stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:08.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.59,0:03:12.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.69,0:03:15.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What if Kagome's butt\ngets deformed!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:16.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,S-Shippo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.97,0:03:19.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:20.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But understand this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:23.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We start up again as soon as\NKagome's butt returns to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:24.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:25.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:26.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:33.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's turning into a downpour.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:35.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's look for shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.59,0:03:41.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't leave me! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:47.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,An evil apparition?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.60,0:03:48.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:51.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Several villagers have already\nbeen killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:54.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Priestess, please put a\nspell on the apparition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:56.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Please!\N- Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.31,0:04:02.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The apparition lives in the misty swamp\nat the top of the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:05.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please, Priestess!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.75,0:04:08.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I understand.\NThe misty swamp, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:21.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So this is the place...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:23.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:26.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's an uncommon air\nabout this place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:53.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:27.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This isn't the place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.46,0:05:32.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have been traveling around looking\nforareas with a demonic aura...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.01,0:05:39.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I have not come across...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.01,0:05:41.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}any sign of Naraku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.59,0:05:53.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}With Naraku's disappearance,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:05:55.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the numberof demons and\napparitions has grown.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:58.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Simply searching forplaces\nwith a demonic aura{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.63,0:06:01.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}is not the answerto\ncapturing Naraku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.60,0:06:07.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:11.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A human?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:14.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He has a serious illness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:16.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He does not have long to live.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:21.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The villagers gave you a fat reward\nforexterminating the demon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:23.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Reward?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.22,0:06:25.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:26.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Any amount will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:29.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Leave all yourmoney.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.79,0:06:31.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't have money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:35.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no temple or shrine\nhereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.23,0:06:39.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're traveling without\na farthing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:42.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you think I lie,\ngo ahead and search me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:46.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you eat\nmist to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:49.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmph... you could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:55.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Never mind then.\NDisappearfrom here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.82,0:07:00.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:01.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.06,0:07:06.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A Sacred Jewel shard?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.20,0:07:11.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That shard is what\nkeeps you alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.13,0:07:13.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:15.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll be seventy next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:21.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If the average man lives 50 years,\NI've lived too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.28,0:07:24.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I can't die yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:27.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As long as I have this\NSacred Jewel shard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:32.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you intend to do\nin that condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:35.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Find my death place...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.39,0:08:09.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Drink this.\NIt'll ease the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.99,0:08:13.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why do you help a\nman like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:16.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You didn't finish\nyour story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:30.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I went searching for a suitable\nplace to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:32.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Suitable place to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:33.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:35.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,From the days of my youth,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:38.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've committed all\nkinds of evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:44.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kansuke, the Mad Killer Rasetsu\nwas quite notorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:50.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I killed... stole... burned...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:52.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I did whatever I felt like doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:57.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I figured I was gonna end up\ndead soon anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.87,0:09:01.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So I lived as I pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.38,0:09:07.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I was a stubborn guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:13.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I got to be old like this...\nand I'm still living.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:16.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:20.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hate growing old.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:23.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I keep forgetting things\nthese days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:27.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I suddenly recall silly things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:31.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When I first saw you,\NI was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.97,0:09:33.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that you look like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.98,0:09:35.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look like who?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.34,0:09:40.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Long ago, I came upon a priestess\nwho looked exactly like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.02,0:09:43.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hername was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:45.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.86,0:09:48.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pure coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.46,0:09:51.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naturally. I'm talking\nabout fifty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:53.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If she were still alive,\nshe'd be an old woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:57.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If she lived...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:02.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well... I heard through the grapevine\nthat she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:06.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And that the Sacred Jewel was\ninterred with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.28,0:10:12.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know how this thing came\nto exist in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.28,0:10:15.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I got it at the very last moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.98,0:10:20.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Were you seeking the Sacred Jewel\nfifty years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:23.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah... Along with a fellow named\NOnigumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.69,0:10:24.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Onigumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.73,0:10:28.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He had a burn scarthat\nwas shaped like a spider.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:34.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now he was a true villain...\NI couldn't compare with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:42.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It'll grant any wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.61,0:10:43.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:47.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's amazing!\NAnd it's called the Shikon Jewel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.72,0:10:49.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In the village overyonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.55,0:10:51.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A priestess named Kikyo\nhas possession of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:55.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then we'll attack this village\ntomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:59.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, Rasetsu... go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:00.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:02.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo has sharp senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:05.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we go in numbers,\nshe'll escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:08.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! Then what'll I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.34,0:11:10.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With your bow and arrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:12.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you can get herfrom a distance\nwith one shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:13.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.08,0:11:16.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:19.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Won't you try it, Rasetsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:22.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whatever I want, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:24.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll be able to drink all\nthe {\i1}sake{\i0} I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.36,0:11:31.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And next, I'll conquer\nthe world!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.83,0:11:40.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I found you! Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.10,0:11:42.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:48.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.38,0:11:50.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Just a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:51.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:54.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A human like you... trying\nto take Kikyo's life...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:55.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've got some nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.45,0:11:58.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you after the Sacred Jewel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:01.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up, demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:10.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I'm no demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:12.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now prepare to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:13.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.27,0:12:16.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! You're a lucky dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:19.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.41,0:12:21.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh! It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:25.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't do anything rough\nwhen I'm around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.39,0:12:37.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.36,0:12:40.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where did they go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:44.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn that Onigumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:48.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He planned to take\nmy men from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.49,0:13:06.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So this is where...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:13.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,B-Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.66,0:13:14.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:18.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:20.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We didn't mean to\nbetray you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:21.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.64,0:13:25.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you come back to me,\NI'll spare your lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:26.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.18,0:13:28.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.08,0:13:30.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where is that Onigumo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.21,0:13:33.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.35,0:13:35.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.38,0:13:38.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Didn't that half-demon\nkill you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.52,0:13:40.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Look at this eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:45.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How dare you set me up\nlike that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.66,0:13:49.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now I'll return the favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:51.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rasetsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:56.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So long, Onigumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:15.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Burn! Burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.76,0:14:17.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:29.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,R-Rasetsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.67,0:14:32.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stubborn fellow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:37.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:39.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Throw him over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:44.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Onigumo, this time you\ncan go get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:47.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:50.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say hello to Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.63,0:14:53.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you threw him over?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:57.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah. To the infernal abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.57,0:15:00.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Infernal abyss... Naraku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:03.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And? What happened afterthat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:04.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That was the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.37,0:15:10.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I stole this Sacred Jewel shard\nrecently from a dying demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:14.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But it won'tgrant my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:17.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It just prolongs my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.49,0:15:21.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and tempts demons to\nconstantly attack me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.92,0:15:28.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Onigumo continues to\nbetray me even in death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:32.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Although, this shard helps\nto ward off those demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.34,0:15:35.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:37.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:41.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Most probably, to get\nthat shard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:42.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ademon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.48,0:15:43.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This demonic aura...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:45.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It couldn't be... Naraku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:48.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, it's not.\NThis is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:15:56.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give it to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.69,0:15:58.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give me the Sacred Jewel shard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:18.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.98,0:16:20.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just what are you to Naraku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:21.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.65,0:16:24.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That unforgivable Naraku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.39,0:16:28.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku severed me from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:30.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Looking like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.49,0:16:34.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a portion of Naraku's body...\nwhich was abandoned?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.90,0:16:36.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Sacred Jewel shard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:38.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I have the shard,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.30,0:16:42.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll be able to secure myself\na properbody.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:44.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.24,0:16:48.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:50.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:54.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A human dares defy me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:58.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give me... the bow and arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.25,0:17:02.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hand overthe Sacred Jewel shard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:05.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You want this so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.24,0:17:23.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That arrow-!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:38.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.29,0:17:42.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How pitiful... saved by a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:47.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However, you're some woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:03.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I got it back foryou.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.15,0:18:07.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have no need forthat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:10.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.26,0:18:15.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However, I have just\none request.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.66,0:18:17.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Request?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:21.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've lived the way I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:24.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However, afterexperiencing\nold age and sickness,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.44,0:18:28.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've become afraid of falling\nto Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:30.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You want to be saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:36.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I heard thateven villains like\nme can find salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:41.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I've traveled in search\nof it as a place forme to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.36,0:18:45.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I guess I won't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.09,0:18:46.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.37,0:18:56.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.04,0:19:01.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iock of hair and bury it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:06.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:10.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's yourname?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:15.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:20.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's a bad joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.31,0:19:35.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The wheel of fortune is\neverin motion...so{\i0} they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.30,0:20:01.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Put this on so\nyou won't catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:05.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've already caught one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:10.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, someone's gossiping\nabout me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:16.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dummy! Who'd gossip about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.49,0:20:19.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good, no fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:23.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you forbeing concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:27.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh... you're starting to get warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.03,0:20:29.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's okay, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.99,0:20:58.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Came all this way\nwith his remains?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:00.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you so much\nfor all yourtrouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.10,0:21:03.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was his dying wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:07.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've heard about this\nplace of purification.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:12.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I believe the priest's name\nwas Hakushin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.34,0:21:14.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.51,0:21:17.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's a temple started\nby this Priest Hakushin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.98,0:21:21.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And if the soul is returned there,\nhe can cleanse any sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.52,0:21:24.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where is this temple?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.99,0:21:26.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mount Hakurei.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:28.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mount Hakurei?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:30.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Beyond this forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.19,0:21:34.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,there's a valley\noverwhich looms Mount Hakurei.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.21,0:21:48.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So that is Mount Hakurei.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.61,0:21:55.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm getting a strange feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.40,0:23:52.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All the fields have been ruined!\NIt's time to act, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.60,0:23:54.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm no Dog God!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.97,0:23:56.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's so hard about\ncatching monkeys?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.67,0:23:58.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why do I have to take\ncare of monkeys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.61,0:24:01.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There! Oh, how cute?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.61,0:24:03.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say, do you want some treats?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.84,0:24:05.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.18,0:24:07.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those baby monkeys have\nused some kind of magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.82,0:24:12.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"The Three Sprites of the Monkey God!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.22,0:24:15.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, stop it!\NDon't use your Wind Tunnel!
